                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The United Nations Representative for India and Pakistan informed the Security
                    Council in a letter of May 29, 1952 that negotiations between India and Pakistan
                    had been renewed (UN doc. S/2649). The negotiations took place in New York
                    between May 29 and July 16, 1952.</p>
            </div>
